WEBVTT

00:06:30.145 --> 00:06:36.680
I'd like to see a thousand
compassionate cities in the next decade

00:06:36.704 --> 00:06:40.932
that remind the rest of the world
what our duty is.

00:06:43.037 --> 00:06:46.931
Always treat all others
as you'd like to be treated yourself.

00:06:55.297 --> 00:06:56.342
[Share and sign
the Charter for Compassion]

00:06:56.362 --> 00:06:58.232
[CharterForCompassion.org]